sequenceDiagram
    participant User
    participant Azure as Azure App Service
    participant API as FastAPI
    participant Models as ML Layer
    participant Agents as Agent Layer
    participant DB as MongoDB

    User->>Azure: request
    Azure->>API: route to endpoint
    alt Forecast
        API->>Models: demand forecast
    else Anomaly
        API->>Models: anomaly check
    else Agent
        API->>Agents: support / sales / analytics
    end
    API->>DB: save operational log
    API-->>Azure: response
    Azure-->>User: JSON output
